1
00:00:23,540 --> 00:00:28,450
♪Like a flock of birds
pressing ever forward♪

2
00:00:28,980 --> 00:00:33,350
♪Stranded on an island
shrouded in heavy mist♪

3
00:00:34,450 --> 00:00:38,410
♪We may seem small
beneath the vast world♪

4
00:00:38,410 --> 00:00:43,680
♪But not once have we felt despair♪

5
00:00:43,970 --> 00:00:46,770
♪We've crossed waves
a thousand layers deep♪

6
00:00:46,770 --> 00:00:49,530
♪Stepped on reefs hidden in the dark♪

7
00:00:49,530 --> 00:00:54,730
♪Facing sharper winds head-on♪

8
00:00:54,730 --> 00:00:57,660
♪Our wounds now stitched
into battle robes♪

9
00:00:57,660 --> 00:01:00,370
♪The long night
is branded by starlight♪

10
00:01:00,370 --> 00:01:05,440
♪We embrace this deep blue together♪

11
00:01:05,590 --> 00:01:10,620
♪At the edge of the vast unknown,
I remain unchanged♪

12
00:01:11,070 --> 00:01:16,540
♪Holding fast with lonely courage,
roaring without fear♪

13
00:01:16,670 --> 00:01:21,850
♪Determined to be
both my friend and my rival♪

14
00:01:22,140 --> 00:01:27,030
♪No one dares to blindly
urge me to turn back♪

15
00:01:27,030 --> 00:01:32,090
♪I choose what I believe is worth it♪

16
00:01:33,300 --> 00:01:38,340
=Rose and Gun=

17
00:01:38,940 --> 00:01:40,980
=Episode 8=

18
00:01:48,537 --> 00:01:49,960
I'll go to the bow to take a look.

19
00:02:15,810 --> 00:02:17,480
I'm taking pictures of the sea.

20
00:02:18,848 --> 00:02:20,720
I won't block you then.
Take the pictures.

21
00:02:20,880 --> 00:02:22,370
You can stand there.

22
00:02:22,370 --> 00:02:23,010
It's okay.

23
00:02:46,871 --> 00:02:48,440
I'm taking pictures of the sea.

24
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:21,240
(City Meteorological Observatory
issued a yellow thunderstorm warning.)

25
00:03:22,720 --> 00:03:23,720
The wind is coming.

26
00:03:27,600 --> 00:03:28,600
Let's go back.

27
00:03:30,320 --> 00:03:30,920
Okay.

28
00:03:33,480 --> 00:03:34,570
So much fuss.

29
00:03:36,290 --> 00:03:37,640
Okay, let's have a drink together.

30
00:03:37,810 --> 00:03:38,640
See you tonight.

31
00:03:41,226 --> 00:03:42,004
Mr. Han.

32
00:03:42,410 --> 00:03:44,040
The female reporter
rented a fishing boat

33
00:03:44,040 --> 00:03:45,480
with a man and went out to sea.

34
00:03:45,920 --> 00:03:47,810
They should be
heading toward Dayan Reef.

35
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:50,250
But they're unlucky.
The wind is picking up at sea,

36
00:03:50,250 --> 00:03:51,640
so they turned back.

37
00:03:54,250 --> 00:03:56,570
What does the man who went to sea

38
00:03:57,250 --> 00:03:58,200
with her do?

39
00:03:59,410 --> 00:04:00,530
It's unclear at the moment.

40
00:04:00,530 --> 00:04:01,693
I'll check it out immediately.

41
00:04:32,930 --> 00:04:35,715
(Tang Xin: Captain Wu, thank you for today.)

42
00:04:49,050 --> 00:04:50,640
You asked me to come in such a hurry,

43
00:04:50,640 --> 00:04:52,560
yet you're on your phone
as soon as I'm here.

44
00:04:52,604 --> 00:04:53,960
Tell me what happened.

45
00:04:59,320 --> 00:05:00,520
Today,

46
00:05:01,690 --> 00:05:02,930
Zong Qing

47
00:05:03,570 --> 00:05:05,250
proposed to me.

48
00:05:10,170 --> 00:05:12,690
Aren't you going to say you found a job?

49
00:05:13,050 --> 00:05:14,280
Why did you get proposed?

50
00:05:14,690 --> 00:05:15,960
What's this reaction?

51
00:05:15,960 --> 00:05:17,280
Shouldn't you be happy for me?

52
00:05:17,293 --> 00:05:19,200
Isn't marriage
more important than finding a job?

53
00:05:19,200 --> 00:05:20,370
What's going on?

54
00:05:20,370 --> 00:05:22,170
Why did you get proposed suddenly?

55
00:05:23,250 --> 00:05:25,640
He proposed to me
when the time was right.

56
00:05:27,280 --> 00:05:28,200
You said yes?

57
00:05:28,810 --> 00:05:30,200
Why not?

58
00:05:30,440 --> 00:05:31,960
What I hate the most

59
00:05:31,960 --> 00:05:33,200
is draggy relationships.

60
00:05:33,204 --> 00:05:35,160
You're just wasting
other people's time and your own.

61
00:05:36,204 --> 00:05:38,520
I want a relationship that goes all in
from the start.

62
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:39,400
Love at first sight,

63
00:05:39,440 --> 00:05:40,640
propose, get married,

64
00:05:40,640 --> 00:05:43,170
and live happily ever after.

65
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:45,250
Lan Yangyang.

66
00:05:45,370 --> 00:05:47,690
Do you really want to get married?

67
00:05:48,280 --> 00:05:49,440
Tell me the truth.

68
00:05:49,760 --> 00:05:50,960
How far have you and Zong Qing

69
00:05:51,320 --> 00:05:52,690
gotten?

70
00:05:53,250 --> 00:05:54,930
What are you thinking?

71
00:05:54,930 --> 00:05:56,960
You think we got married
because I'm pregnant, are you?

72
00:05:57,200 --> 00:05:59,130
No, absolutely not.

73
00:05:59,440 --> 00:06:01,520
I just want to marry Zong Qing.

74
00:06:01,520 --> 00:06:03,170
Is it so hard to understand

75
00:06:03,170 --> 00:06:04,337
that I want to marry for love?

76
00:06:04,520 --> 00:06:06,320
Put your love aside for now.

77
00:06:06,520 --> 00:06:08,570
Marriage is different from dating.

78
00:06:08,570 --> 00:06:10,000
There are a lot of real-world issues.

79
00:06:10,004 --> 00:06:11,170
Have you thought it through?

80
00:06:11,170 --> 00:06:12,520
I've thought it through.

81
00:06:12,640 --> 00:06:14,760
I'll tell my parents later.

82
00:06:14,760 --> 00:06:17,400
Tomorrow, I'll go wedding dress
and wedding ring shopping.

83
00:06:20,690 --> 00:06:21,320
Speaking of,

84
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:22,840
I have something else to tell you.

85
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:23,730
Bridesmaid duties.

86
00:06:24,440 --> 00:06:26,010
Just being a bridesmaid

87
00:06:26,010 --> 00:06:27,930
is a waste of talent

88
00:06:27,930 --> 00:06:29,730
for Miss Tang.

89
00:06:31,840 --> 00:06:33,010
I also want you

90
00:06:33,200 --> 00:06:36,400
to help me plan
the most romantic wedding in the world.

91
00:06:40,080 --> 00:06:43,370
Help me prepare everything

92
00:06:43,370 --> 00:06:45,490
for the beach, forest

93
00:06:45,640 --> 00:06:46,640
and meadow-style venues.

94
00:06:46,640 --> 00:06:47,570
Handle the arrangements.

95
00:06:47,570 --> 00:06:48,250
By the way,

96
00:06:48,250 --> 00:06:49,370
I also want to prepare

97
00:06:49,400 --> 00:06:50,960
a confession video for the wedding.

98
00:06:50,960 --> 00:06:51,730
Of course

99
00:06:51,730 --> 00:06:52,960
I'm counting

100
00:06:52,960 --> 00:06:54,760
on my favorite Miss Tang for this.

101
00:06:54,760 --> 00:06:57,520
I need you to put
that dream wedding on hold

102
00:06:57,520 --> 00:06:58,930
for now.

103
00:06:58,982 --> 00:07:01,050
Let me ask you.
How many relationships have you had?

104
00:07:02,010 --> 00:07:04,080
Just this time, right?

105
00:07:04,610 --> 00:07:07,050
You couldn't even tell
that someone had a crush on you.

106
00:07:07,050 --> 00:07:08,170
Zong Qing's

107
00:07:08,400 --> 00:07:09,570
dating experience probably

108
00:07:09,610 --> 00:07:10,880
isn't much different
from yours.

109
00:07:10,880 --> 00:07:13,610
How dare you two get a shotgun wedding?

110
00:07:13,690 --> 00:07:16,010
One dared to propose
and the other dared to say yes.

111
00:07:19,760 --> 00:07:20,840
Tang Xin.

112
00:07:21,080 --> 00:07:22,690
You're a buzzkill.

113
00:07:23,960 --> 00:07:26,170
Either way, I won't regret it.

114
00:07:27,840 --> 00:07:29,490
As long as Zong Qing is around,

115
00:07:30,490 --> 00:07:31,810
I'm not afraid of anything.

116
00:07:36,537 --> 00:07:37,930
Why are you looking at me like that?

117
00:07:37,930 --> 00:07:39,930
Did I misjudge you?

118
00:07:40,400 --> 00:07:42,810
Lan Yangyang, you're so cool.

119
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:44,490
I don't care.

120
00:07:44,640 --> 00:07:45,880
You're now

121
00:07:46,050 --> 00:07:48,130
my wedding planner.

122
00:07:51,170 --> 00:07:52,280
When did she start dating?

123
00:07:52,280 --> 00:07:53,320
How come we don't know?

124
00:07:53,320 --> 00:07:55,315
We really don't know
when she started dating.

125
00:07:55,930 --> 00:07:57,570
They were having a secret relationship.

126
00:07:57,570 --> 00:07:58,610
Besides you two,

127
00:07:58,610 --> 00:08:00,182
Mr. Lan and his wife don't know either.

128
00:08:00,200 --> 00:08:02,390
Let's see how Lan Yangyang explains it
when she gets home.

129
00:08:03,250 --> 00:08:05,960
Lan Weiguo is so lucky.

130
00:08:06,730 --> 00:08:07,840
He just sits at home

131
00:08:07,840 --> 00:08:09,370
and somehow gains a son-in-law.

132
00:08:10,280 --> 00:08:12,080
Dad, what's that stance?

133
00:08:12,080 --> 00:08:14,170
Why do you seem relieved?

134
00:08:14,490 --> 00:08:16,200
Does my expression seem relieved?

135
00:08:18,010 --> 00:08:19,880
Hey, my little troublemaker.

136
00:08:20,093 --> 00:08:21,960
If you're half as easy to deal with
as Yangyang,

137
00:08:21,960 --> 00:08:23,320
I'll be relieved.

138
00:08:23,840 --> 00:08:25,170
Look at Yangyang.

139
00:08:25,960 --> 00:08:27,880
She quietly pulled off something huge.

140
00:08:28,810 --> 00:08:29,880
What about you?

141
00:08:30,520 --> 00:08:32,160
Have you and Wu Si

142
00:08:33,800 --> 00:08:35,280
- met?
- Dad.

143
00:08:35,520 --> 00:08:37,010
Have you contacted him?

144
00:08:37,450 --> 00:08:39,090
I'm a career-oriented woman.

145
00:08:39,090 --> 00:08:40,970
I don't have the time to contact him.

146
00:08:41,520 --> 00:08:42,280
I'll go.

147
00:08:45,370 --> 00:08:46,640
Career-oriented?

148
00:08:50,640 --> 00:08:51,760
Yes.

149
00:09:07,040 --> 00:09:07,610
Dad.

150
00:09:08,040 --> 00:09:08,680
Mom.

151
00:09:10,760 --> 00:09:12,210
I'll formally report it to you.

152
00:09:13,210 --> 00:09:14,400
This is Big Big Wolf.

153
00:09:16,400 --> 00:09:17,560
His name is Zong Qing.

154
00:09:18,090 --> 00:09:19,450
He's from the Marine Corps.

155
00:09:19,610 --> 00:09:21,730
Blue Blade Special Ops Team
in the Marine Corps.

156
00:09:22,920 --> 00:09:23,490
Yes.

157
00:09:24,450 --> 00:09:27,382
He's excellent. He joined the Party
in his second year of enlistment.

158
00:09:27,426 --> 00:09:29,382
He's also been awarded
third-class merit twice.

159
00:09:29,970 --> 00:09:33,210
He even saved a child from drowning
before proposing.

160
00:09:33,850 --> 00:09:35,400
When I first met him,

161
00:09:35,520 --> 00:09:36,850
I liked him very much.

162
00:09:37,160 --> 00:09:39,800
I think he's handsome. Just like...

163
00:09:42,330 --> 00:09:44,010
Just like Dad when he was young.

164
00:09:45,920 --> 00:09:48,160
He understands me, is protective of me,

165
00:09:48,560 --> 00:09:50,730
tolerates me and treats me well.

166
00:09:52,250 --> 00:09:53,730
That's why I'm willing to marry him.

167
00:09:58,560 --> 00:09:59,560
Mom and Dad.

168
00:10:01,250 --> 00:10:03,250
Say something.

169
00:10:04,010 --> 00:10:05,450
We're serious.

170
00:10:06,280 --> 00:10:06,850
You...

171
00:10:08,090 --> 00:10:09,400
What do you want us to say?

172
00:10:09,400 --> 00:10:10,400
You're serious?

173
00:10:10,560 --> 00:10:12,130
It's a big deal.

174
00:10:12,130 --> 00:10:14,004
You can't just go ahead
and tell us afterward.

175
00:10:14,130 --> 00:10:16,090
But it happened suddenly.

176
00:10:17,520 --> 00:10:19,130
I won't regret it anyway.

177
00:10:19,880 --> 00:10:20,850
And I never will.

178
00:10:26,450 --> 00:10:27,130
I really...

179
00:10:28,970 --> 00:10:29,610
Yangyang.

180
00:10:31,890 --> 00:10:32,970
I'm sorry.

181
00:10:33,610 --> 00:10:34,370
I

182
00:10:34,782 --> 00:10:36,271
shouldn't have looked at your phone.

183
00:10:36,730 --> 00:10:37,370
Dad.

184
00:10:38,370 --> 00:10:39,370
Don't do this.

185
00:10:39,370 --> 00:10:40,370
I was wrong.

186
00:10:41,880 --> 00:10:43,800
I shouldn't have
kept delaying the job search

187
00:10:44,400 --> 00:10:46,800
and not told you
that I have a boyfriend.

188
00:10:47,970 --> 00:10:51,130
I shouldn't have decided to get engaged
without asking you.

189
00:10:52,730 --> 00:10:53,730
I've

190
00:10:54,450 --> 00:10:56,010
figured out what you should do

191
00:10:56,400 --> 00:10:58,010
after graduation.

192
00:10:58,680 --> 00:10:59,970
You should have

193
00:11:00,400 --> 00:11:03,280
the right to choose
your own future and career.

194
00:11:04,370 --> 00:11:05,970
But what I don't understand

195
00:11:06,026 --> 00:11:07,515
is why you have never told us

196
00:11:07,970 --> 00:11:09,610
what you actually want

197
00:11:09,800 --> 00:11:11,130
after so many years?

198
00:11:11,800 --> 00:11:12,610
You

199
00:11:13,850 --> 00:11:16,160
didn't even tell us
about something as important

200
00:11:16,226 --> 00:11:17,626
as dating or getting engaged.

201
00:11:21,520 --> 00:11:23,010
We're not old-fashioned parents.

202
00:11:23,450 --> 00:11:25,130
We're not against you dating freely,

203
00:11:25,400 --> 00:11:27,250
but we can't just entrust our daughter

204
00:11:27,730 --> 00:11:28,730
to a man

205
00:11:29,010 --> 00:11:30,920
whom we haven't even formally met.

206
00:11:32,520 --> 00:11:33,760
Have you thought it through?

207
00:11:34,330 --> 00:11:37,970
I'm willful, spoiled,

208
00:11:38,520 --> 00:11:39,880
jobless

209
00:11:40,130 --> 00:11:42,130
and can't do housework.

210
00:11:42,130 --> 00:11:44,090
- I don't care.
- I don't care.

211
00:11:44,090 --> 00:11:46,090
- Marry me!
- Marry me!

212
00:11:46,800 --> 00:11:48,130
You've nailed the imitation.

213
00:11:48,130 --> 00:11:49,560
- Yes, of course.
- Yes.

214
00:11:49,937 --> 00:11:51,370
- Did I imitate him well?
- Yes.

215
00:11:51,370 --> 00:11:53,800
- Marry me!
- Marry me!

216
00:11:55,370 --> 00:11:56,040
Dad.

217
00:11:58,250 --> 00:11:59,920
Whether it's my career choice

218
00:12:00,370 --> 00:12:01,760
or relationship,

219
00:12:03,490 --> 00:12:05,130
I've never thought

220
00:12:05,130 --> 00:12:06,800
about deliberately hiding it from you.

221
00:12:08,850 --> 00:12:10,490
I was really scared to tell you.

222
00:12:11,610 --> 00:12:13,680
I know you still consider me a child,

223
00:12:14,370 --> 00:12:16,160
arranging this and that for me.

224
00:12:18,730 --> 00:12:20,130
But I have grown up.

225
00:12:21,370 --> 00:12:23,040
I want to go my own way now.

226
00:12:23,370 --> 00:12:24,680
Like Xin.

227
00:12:26,280 --> 00:12:27,370
Like Zong Qing.

228
00:12:29,160 --> 00:12:30,610
Do what I want to do.

229
00:12:33,490 --> 00:12:35,010
Marry the one I love.

230
00:12:36,920 --> 00:12:37,920
Do you understand

231
00:12:40,915 --> 00:12:42,730
what being in a military marriage
involves?

232
00:12:43,730 --> 00:12:45,850
Do you know what it means

233
00:12:46,010 --> 00:12:47,250
to marry a frontline soldier?

234
00:12:48,610 --> 00:12:51,160
Do you know the consequences
of an impulsive marriage?

235
00:12:53,130 --> 00:12:54,280
You just graduated.

236
00:12:54,626 --> 00:12:56,560
Zong Qing has just been enlisted
for a few years.

237
00:12:57,730 --> 00:12:58,370
Have you two

238
00:12:58,370 --> 00:13:00,250
really prepared yourselves
for the future?

239
00:13:01,800 --> 00:13:02,680
Married life

240
00:13:02,920 --> 00:13:05,040
isn't as romantic as you imagine.

241
00:13:06,250 --> 00:13:06,800
You...

242
00:13:08,490 --> 00:13:10,370
Are you capable of handling it?

243
00:13:18,730 --> 00:13:19,280
Dad.

244
00:13:19,920 --> 00:13:22,280
I didn't have time
to consider all of that,

245
00:13:25,010 --> 00:13:27,370
but I'm sure that Zong Qing is the one.

246
00:13:29,040 --> 00:13:31,680
He's kind, dependable, and responsible.

247
00:13:32,400 --> 00:13:34,010
He loves his job.

248
00:13:34,271 --> 00:13:36,040
He also loves
the honor of being a soldier.

249
00:13:36,040 --> 00:13:37,010
He loves me more.

250
00:13:39,250 --> 00:13:40,370
So I believe him.

251
00:13:40,610 --> 00:13:41,680
I'm not afraid of anything.

252
00:13:52,730 --> 00:13:53,730
Move back home.

253
00:13:55,370 --> 00:13:57,160
Stop staying in someone else's house.

254
00:13:57,160 --> 00:13:58,130
It's inappropriate.

255
00:14:04,610 --> 00:14:05,400
Yangyang.

256
00:14:07,400 --> 00:14:08,280
Come here.

257
00:14:19,490 --> 00:14:20,730
Do you really want

258
00:14:23,090 --> 00:14:24,210
to marry a soldier?

259
00:14:28,330 --> 00:14:29,640
I want to marry Zong Qing.

260
00:14:36,680 --> 00:14:37,800
You've grown up.

261
00:14:43,090 --> 00:14:43,970
You've grown up.

262
00:14:51,370 --> 00:14:53,004
I'll congratulate you first.

263
00:15:13,250 --> 00:15:14,370
Hello, Miss Tang?

264
00:15:14,400 --> 00:15:15,130
What's wrong?

265
00:15:15,450 --> 00:15:16,210
Captain Wu.

266
00:15:17,730 --> 00:15:18,490
Today,

267
00:15:19,040 --> 00:15:20,730
Zong Qing proposed to Yangyang.

268
00:15:20,871 --> 00:15:22,040
You knew about this, right?

269
00:15:22,370 --> 00:15:23,160
Yes.

270
00:15:24,490 --> 00:15:25,490
What do you think?

271
00:15:26,640 --> 00:15:27,760
I agree, of course.

272
00:15:28,400 --> 00:15:29,760
Both parties are willing.

273
00:15:29,760 --> 00:15:30,680
What can I say?

274
00:15:30,760 --> 00:15:32,010
What? You have an issue with it?

275
00:15:32,970 --> 00:15:34,330
It's not that I have an issue.

276
00:15:34,920 --> 00:15:36,610
But marriage is a big deal.

277
00:15:36,850 --> 00:15:39,370
I have to help her
screen him a little more.

278
00:15:40,130 --> 00:15:41,610
Zong Qing is my subordinate,

279
00:15:41,880 --> 00:15:43,210
but I will never favor him.

280
00:15:43,640 --> 00:15:44,490
