565
00:33:55,940 --> 00:33:56,940
I take it back.

566
00:33:57,140 --> 00:33:58,940
You're a general among the bad options.

567
00:34:07,860 --> 00:34:08,540
Tang Xin.

568
00:34:09,220 --> 00:34:09,900
Captain Wu.

569
00:34:10,540 --> 00:34:11,940
Why did you call me suddenly?

570
00:34:13,220 --> 00:34:14,260
Nothing.

571
00:34:14,740 --> 00:34:17,220
I wonder if I can come over
for an interview tomorrow.

572
00:34:17,380 --> 00:34:18,820
Yes, come by anytime.

573
00:34:19,940 --> 00:34:20,540
Okay.

574
00:34:21,860 --> 00:34:23,020
Let me know anytime

575
00:34:23,060 --> 00:34:23,860
if you need help.

576
00:34:24,020 --> 00:34:24,900
I'll sort it out.

577
00:34:26,540 --> 00:34:28,020
Any help?

578
00:34:28,260 --> 00:34:29,020
Yes.

579
00:34:31,060 --> 00:34:32,860
I hope you'll have my back

580
00:34:32,860 --> 00:34:34,220
during tomorrow's interview.

581
00:34:34,220 --> 00:34:36,260
Don't sneak off again like last time.

582
00:34:36,500 --> 00:34:37,780
I'll stay with you.

583
00:34:38,460 --> 00:34:39,420
Any other questions?

584
00:34:42,340 --> 00:34:43,740
Also...

585
00:34:48,460 --> 00:34:50,420
Nothing. See you tomorrow.

586
00:34:57,020 --> 00:34:58,260
Also,

587
00:34:59,980 --> 00:35:01,260
I really want to know

588
00:35:02,500 --> 00:35:04,780
if you were the one
who saved me at Dayan Reef...

589
00:35:13,020 --> 00:35:14,020
I hope it was you.

590
00:35:20,940 --> 00:35:21,500
Dad.

591
00:35:21,740 --> 00:35:22,260
Mom.

592
00:35:22,940 --> 00:35:23,780
You're not eating?

593
00:35:24,260 --> 00:35:26,420
No, I'm trying to lose weight.
I'll go back to my room.

594
00:35:26,620 --> 00:35:27,140
You...

595
00:35:27,140 --> 00:35:28,820
You're skipping meals
just to lose weight.

596
00:35:28,826 --> 00:35:29,620
It's time for dinner.

597
00:35:29,700 --> 00:35:30,820
Come chat with us

598
00:35:30,820 --> 00:35:31,940
for a bit.

599
00:35:31,940 --> 00:35:32,740
Yeah.

600
00:35:32,940 --> 00:35:34,020
I'm a little tired.

601
00:35:34,020 --> 00:35:35,420
I want to go back and lie down.

602
00:35:35,420 --> 00:35:38,026
I have to go to the military camp
for an interview tomorrow morning.

603
00:35:41,940 --> 00:35:43,940
Is Wu Si going to be
at tomorrow's interview

604
00:35:44,260 --> 00:35:45,620
at the military camp?

605
00:35:45,940 --> 00:35:46,620
Is he?

606
00:35:48,700 --> 00:35:50,380
I guess so.

607
00:35:51,315 --> 00:35:53,426
Why don't you
take advantage of this opportunity

608
00:35:53,493 --> 00:35:54,715
to spend some time together?

609
00:35:54,740 --> 00:35:56,004
How are you two getting along?

610
00:35:56,820 --> 00:35:57,420
Well...

611
00:35:58,460 --> 00:36:00,380
It's alright. It's been good.

612
00:36:00,900 --> 00:36:02,380
How is it good? Hurry and tell us.

613
00:36:04,020 --> 00:36:04,780
Well.

614
00:36:06,140 --> 00:36:08,020
Everything has been pretty good.

615
00:36:08,220 --> 00:36:10,500
If it's been pretty good, hurry up then.

616
00:36:11,300 --> 00:36:12,740
You're killing us with the suspense.

617
00:36:12,820 --> 00:36:14,460
I can't rush it.

618
00:36:15,100 --> 00:36:17,780
It's not like I can see or touch him
right now anyway.

619
00:36:19,260 --> 00:36:20,420
Are you embarrassed?

620
00:36:20,420 --> 00:36:21,940
It's not like you.

621
00:36:23,260 --> 00:36:24,780
Who's embarrassed? Dad.

622
00:36:24,937 --> 00:36:25,980
Alright, I'm done talking.

623
00:36:25,980 --> 00:36:27,730
I'm going back
to work on my interview script.

624
00:36:27,737 --> 00:36:28,226
Enjoy dinner.

625
00:36:35,380 --> 00:36:36,420
I think there's a chance.

626
00:36:37,740 --> 00:36:39,420
Maybe they'll really set sail.

627
00:36:40,140 --> 00:36:41,260
Look at her.

628
00:36:41,700 --> 00:36:42,460
She was blushing.

629
00:36:43,900 --> 00:36:44,460
Great.

630
00:36:47,620 --> 00:36:48,500
It's great.

631
00:36:51,420 --> 00:36:52,220
Where are they?

632
00:36:53,420 --> 00:36:54,260
No idea.

633
00:36:54,540 --> 00:36:56,340
I only saw Yi Nanwang when I came in.

634
00:36:56,500 --> 00:36:57,500
He was eating super fast.

635
00:36:57,500 --> 00:36:58,780
I wonder what he's up to next.

636
00:36:58,980 --> 00:36:59,780
It's a bit strange.

637
00:37:00,626 --> 00:37:02,740
You not going home on the weekend
is strange too.

638
00:37:03,293 --> 00:37:04,826
I have some work to do back at the unit.

639
00:37:04,848 --> 00:37:05,980
Zijian will pick me up later.

640
00:37:06,671 --> 00:37:08,020
I don't care when he picks you up.

641
00:37:08,020 --> 00:37:09,271
Your leave is approved anyway.

642
00:37:09,293 --> 00:37:10,220
Have a great weekend.

643
00:37:11,420 --> 00:37:12,420
Thanks, Captain.

644
00:37:23,260 --> 00:37:23,980
Hello, Mom?

645
00:37:25,220 --> 00:37:25,980
Zijian.

646
00:37:26,460 --> 00:37:28,540
Where did your work trip take you?

647
00:37:28,940 --> 00:37:30,300
It's been so long.

648
00:37:30,700 --> 00:37:31,780
Mom, this time I...

649
00:37:35,260 --> 00:37:37,460
This time
I've got to go to several places.

650
00:37:38,060 --> 00:37:39,260
It'll take a while.

651
00:37:40,340 --> 00:37:41,860
You're acting weird.

652
00:37:42,220 --> 00:37:43,260
What's going on?

653
00:37:48,940 --> 00:37:50,140
I'll tell you the truth.

654
00:37:50,620 --> 00:37:51,620
Lately I've been

655
00:37:51,620 --> 00:37:53,380
busy with a job transfer.

656
00:37:53,460 --> 00:37:55,740
I'm planning to transfer
to Wenzhou Marine Museum.

657
00:37:55,900 --> 00:37:57,290
You're transferring to Wenzhou?

658
00:37:57,540 --> 00:37:58,370
That's a big deal.

659
00:37:58,380 --> 00:37:59,740
Why didn't you discuss it with me?

660
00:38:01,940 --> 00:38:03,980
I didn't want you to worry.

661
00:38:04,820 --> 00:38:05,940
Mom, listen.

662
00:38:06,260 --> 00:38:08,420
Wenzhou is a great place.

663
00:38:08,780 --> 00:38:10,020
Wenzhou Marine Museum

664
00:38:10,020 --> 00:38:11,540
has good career opportunities.

665
00:38:11,820 --> 00:38:13,140
Once I get there,

666
00:38:13,220 --> 00:38:15,300
I can really show what I'm capable of.

667
00:38:15,980 --> 00:38:17,260
Just wait for my good news.

668
00:38:17,500 --> 00:38:18,940
Once everything is settled,

669
00:38:18,940 --> 00:38:19,980
I'll report back to you.

670
00:38:22,270 --> 00:38:23,700
Wenzhou has opportunities?

671
00:38:23,700 --> 00:38:25,820
Wang Chen's in Wenzhou too.

672
00:38:26,280 --> 00:38:27,860
Alright, forget it.

673
00:38:29,420 --> 00:38:29,980
Hello?

674
00:38:37,380 --> 00:38:38,060
Captain Zong.

675
00:38:38,860 --> 00:38:40,140
We wear the same uniform,

676
00:38:40,426 --> 00:38:42,300
but how come
it doesn't look the same on me?

677
00:38:42,300 --> 00:38:43,300
Save it.

678
00:38:43,540 --> 00:38:45,604
A few more years in service,
and you'll get there.

679
00:38:48,060 --> 00:38:48,820
Attention!

680
00:38:51,020 --> 00:38:52,020
- Captain.
- Captain.

681
00:38:56,620 --> 00:38:58,930
Yi Nanwang, Wang Chen said

682
00:38:58,930 --> 00:39:00,540
you were flustered at breakfast.

683
00:39:00,915 --> 00:39:02,780
Are you just here
to see Captain Zong get ready?

684
00:39:04,150 --> 00:39:05,130
No, Captain.

685
00:39:05,420 --> 00:39:07,500
Captain Zong's
going to Yangyang's house today.

686
00:39:10,804 --> 00:39:13,248
So that's why you've been pestering me
about your outfit

687
00:39:13,271 --> 00:39:14,020
all day yesterday.

688
00:39:15,260 --> 00:39:15,820
Report.

689
00:39:16,100 --> 00:39:17,620
I'll take Yi Nanwang to the library.

690
00:39:18,300 --> 00:39:18,860
Go.

691
00:39:25,537 --> 00:39:26,740
Tell me how you're feeling.

692
00:39:28,020 --> 00:39:30,100
Honestly? A bit scared.

693
00:39:34,780 --> 00:39:35,780
Marines

694
00:39:37,271 --> 00:39:38,804
don't know the meaning of fear.

695
00:39:40,140 --> 00:39:41,060
You don't get it.

696
00:39:41,060 --> 00:39:42,820
Yangyang told me
her dad is super strict.

697
00:39:43,540 --> 00:39:44,260
Think about it.

698
00:39:44,780 --> 00:39:46,340
I proposed without asking him first.

699
00:39:47,020 --> 00:39:48,380
He is even blaming me

700
00:39:48,380 --> 00:39:49,737
for Yang's quitting being a doctor.

701
00:39:49,737 --> 00:39:50,640
Anyone would be scared.

702
00:39:52,540 --> 00:39:53,540
I think

703
00:39:54,300 --> 00:39:55,580
he has already made up his mind

704
00:39:56,540 --> 00:39:57,980
if he invited you over.

705
00:39:57,980 --> 00:39:59,820
Just relax. You'll be fine.

706
00:40:03,060 --> 00:40:04,660
I'll do anything for Yangyang.

707
00:40:06,140 --> 00:40:08,460
You're meeting your father-in-law,
not going into battle.

708
00:40:08,493 --> 00:40:10,100
Where's your courage from the proposal?

709
00:40:10,180 --> 00:40:12,420
Easy for you to say.

710
00:40:12,826 --> 00:40:15,060
Do you think every father-in-law
is like Captain Tang?

711
00:40:36,300 --> 00:40:36,940
Captain Wu.

712
00:40:38,340 --> 00:40:38,980
Miss Tang.

713
00:40:50,493 --> 00:40:51,540
Why are you here already?

714
00:40:51,540 --> 00:40:52,871
I was just about to pick you up.

715
00:40:56,300 --> 00:40:58,300
I've been
mentally preparing myself outside.

716
00:40:58,404 --> 00:40:59,940
I didn't expect your house to be here.

717
00:41:00,020 --> 00:41:01,420
Is it Zong Qing?

718
00:41:01,780 --> 00:41:02,540
Mom, hurry.

719
00:41:04,780 --> 00:41:05,940
Let me introduce you.

720
00:41:06,060 --> 00:41:07,500
This is Zong Qing.

721
00:41:07,540 --> 00:41:08,220
This is my mom.

722
00:41:08,540 --> 00:41:09,300
Hello, Ma'am.

723
00:41:10,580 --> 00:41:11,540
Hello.

724
00:41:12,500 --> 00:41:13,180
Have a seat.

725
00:41:17,180 --> 00:41:17,820
Come on.

726
00:41:21,900 --> 00:41:22,500
Dad.

727
00:41:25,540 --> 00:41:26,700
Greetings, Chief.

728
00:41:26,700 --> 00:41:27,620
This is my dad.

729
00:41:28,140 --> 00:41:29,020
This is Zong Qing.

730
00:41:31,940 --> 00:41:32,700
At ease.

731
00:41:32,700 --> 00:41:33,420
Yes.

732
00:41:34,900 --> 00:41:36,020
Welcome to our home.

733
00:41:37,020 --> 00:41:38,020
Thank you, Chief.

734
00:41:39,820 --> 00:41:40,780
No need to be so formal.

735
00:41:40,780 --> 00:41:42,060
We're at home, not the military.

736
00:41:42,220 --> 00:41:43,300
You can relax a little.

737
00:41:44,820 --> 00:41:45,500
How tall are you?

738
00:41:45,900 --> 00:41:46,860
Reporting, Chief.

739
00:41:46,980 --> 00:41:48,100
1.88 meters with shoes on.

740
00:41:48,820 --> 00:41:49,820
I knew it.

741
00:41:50,900 --> 00:41:51,860
1.88?

742
00:41:51,860 --> 00:41:53,204
Go wash your hands. Time to eat.

743
00:41:53,460 --> 00:41:54,020
Yes.

744
00:42:00,500 --> 00:42:03,100
Why didn't you tell me your dad was...

745
00:42:05,500 --> 00:42:06,660
You never asked.

746
00:42:25,020 --> 00:42:28,500
♪The vast sky and sea,
this deep blue expanse♪

747
00:42:29,190 --> 00:42:32,460
♪So deep, so boundless♪

748
00:42:32,800 --> 00:42:35,970
♪Just like your arms♪

749
00:42:36,460 --> 00:42:39,580
♪Shielding me from the dark clouds♪

750
00:42:39,870 --> 00:42:43,510
♪Always bearing it all in silence♪

751
00:42:43,510 --> 00:42:49,930
♪Even the long, long road gives me peace
when you're there♪

752
00:42:50,430 --> 00:42:54,830
♪Not one to show romance
in front of others♪

753
00:42:55,290 --> 00:42:58,380
♪You speak of dreams
with such calm simplicity♪

754
00:42:59,170 --> 00:43:03,970
♪But I know your heart
holds much deeper hopes♪

755
00:43:06,240 --> 00:43:08,080
♪I truly understand♪

756
00:43:08,570 --> 00:43:12,760
♪You speak of love so slowly♪

757
00:43:13,010 --> 00:43:18,980
♪But your eyes have already
told me everything♪

758
00:43:19,486 --> 00:43:22,176
♪Using up all my fortune♪

759
00:43:22,180 --> 00:43:26,580
♪Just to trade a lifetime with you♪

760
00:43:26,670 --> 00:43:28,890
♪Thank you for awakening♪

761
00:43:28,900 --> 00:43:33,980
♪The courage once hidden in my fear♪

762
00:43:34,120 --> 00:43:37,310
♪Turning every chance into certainty♪

763
00:43:37,640 --> 00:43:41,170
♪Turning every tie into companionship♪

764
00:43:41,250 --> 00:43:46,220
♪Blooming into brilliance
for all the years to come♪

765
00:43:46,220 --> 00:43:50,210
♪No one can tear us apart♪

766
00:43:50,400 --> 00:43:53,750
♪Each time my palm feels warmth again♪

767
00:43:54,010 --> 00:43:59,350
♪The memories return,
and I'm no longer alone♪

768
00:44:00,240 --> 00:44:04,230
♪No matter how far
across time and space♪

769
00:44:04,480 --> 00:44:07,880
♪My longing reaches you in silence♪

770
00:44:08,000 --> 00:44:12,530
♪No need to call out loudly♪

771
00:44:12,530 --> 00:44:15,200
♪No matter how much it takes♪

772
00:44:15,220 --> 00:44:19,630
♪To bring this drifting heart to shore♪

773
00:44:19,630 --> 00:44:22,890
♪Thank you for standing behind me♪

774
00:44:22,910 --> 00:44:26,960
♪Lighting up the darkness and despair♪

775
00:44:26,960 --> 00:44:30,430
♪The bigger the world,
the lonelier it feels♪

776
00:44:30,430 --> 00:44:34,200
♪Only by your side♪

777
00:44:34,210 --> 00:44:41,290
♪Can I truly feel this warmth inside♪
